text.section:
The person contracting with the city shall agree to:
Acquire ownership of the bridge or portion thereof, unless it has already acquired such ownership;
Operate and maintain the bridge;
Collect tolls for traffic over the bridge or portion of bridge;
Subject to the provisions of KRS 181.520, apply the revenues of the bridge to the amortization of the cost of the bridge or portion of bridge; and
Turn over the bridge or portion of bridge to the city upon completion of the amortization.
